author: The Current
description:
Lucius talk about "domesticity" and what it means to them
Support The Current: https://support.mpr.org/youtube or hit the Thanks button

On Friday, May 9, Lucius were at the Palace Theatre in St. Paul as part of The Gold Rush Tour in support of their self-titled album, released just days earlier on May 2. Holly Laessig and Jess Wolfe took time to talk about how the theme of "domesticity" emerged as the album came together.

Lucius’ 2025 self-titled album is available on @FantasyRecordings.

Guests
Holly Laessig and Jess Wolfe of @Luciusyt
